#. module: dropshipping
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:dropshipping.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Automated Sales Funnels</strong> – Maximize conversions with the "
"<strong>Marketing Automation App</strong>, guiding potential buyers "
"seamlessly from interest to purchase."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ຊ່ອງທາງການຂາຍແບບອັດຕະໂນມັດ</strong> – ເພີ່ມອັດຕາການປ່ຽນເປັນຍອດຂາຍດ້ວຍ <strong>"
"ແອັບການຕະຫຼາດແບບອັດຕະໂນມັດ</strong>, ເຊິ່ງຈະນຳພາຜູ້ຊື້ທີ່ມີທ່າແຮງຕັ້ງແຕ່ເລີ່ມສົນໃຈຈົນເຖິງການສັ່ງຊື້ຢ່າງບໍ່"
"ມີສະດຸດ."

#. module: dropshipping
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:dropshipping.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Email Campaigns That Convert</strong> – Use the <strong>Email "
"Marketing App</strong> to send newsletters, promotions, and updates straight"
" to your customers' inboxes."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ແຄມເປນອີເມວທີ່ສ້າງຍອດຂາຍ</strong> – ໃຊ້ <strong>ແອັບການຕະຫຼາດຜ່ານອີເມວ</"
"strong> ເພື່ອສົ່ງຈົດໝາຍຂ່າວ, ໂປຣໂມຊັນ ແລະ ການອັບເດດຕ່າງໆ ໄປຫາອີເມວຂອງລູກຄ້າໂດຍກົງ."

#. module: dropshipping
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:dropshipping.ir_ui_view_1661
msgid ""
"<strong>Find the perfect case for your phone – durable, stylish, and built "
"for everyday life.</strong>"
msgstr ""
"<strong>ຊອກຫາກາບໂທລະສັບທີ່ເໝາະສົມທີ່ສຸດສຳລັບທ່ານ – ທົນທານ, ມີສະໄຕລ໌ ແລະ ອອກແບບມາເພື່ອຊີວິດປະຈ"
"ຳວັນ.</strong>"

#. module: dropshipping
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:dropshipping.ir_ui_view_1661
msgid "<strong>Japanese collection</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>ຄໍເລັກຊັນຍີ່ປຸ່ນ</strong>"

#. module: dropshipping
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:dropshipping.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>One-Click Confirmation:</strong> Review and confirm purchase orders "
"instantly."
msgstr "<strong>ຢືນຢັນໃນຄລິກດຽວ:</strong> ກວດສອບ ແລະ ຢືນຢັນໃບສັ່ງຊື້ໄດ້ທັນທີ."

#. module: dropshipping
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:dropshipping.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Seamless Supplier Communication:</strong> Send orders to your "
"supplier in just one click, ensuring smooth and timely fulfillment."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ການສື່ສານກັບຜູ້ສະໜອງຢ່າງບໍ່ມີສະດຸດ:</strong> ສົ່ງໃບສັ່ງຊື້ໄປຫາຜູ້ສະໜອງຂອງທ່ານໃນຄລິກດຽວ, ເ"
"ພື່ອຮັບປະກັນການຈັດສົ່ງທີ່ວ່ອງໄວ ແລະ ຕາມກຳນົດເວລາ."

#. module: dropshipping
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:dropshipping.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Social Media Made Simple</strong> – Schedule and manage posts "
"effortlessly with the <strong>Social Marketing App</strong> to keep your "
"audience engaged."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ສື່ສັງຄົມອອນລາຍທີ່ເຮັດໃຫ້ເປັນເລື່ອງງ່າຍ</strong> – ວາງແຜນ ແລະ ຈັດການໂພສໄດ້ຢ່າງສະບາຍດ້"
"ວຍ <strong>ແອັບການຕະຫຼາດຜ່ານສື່ສັງຄົມ</strong> ເພື່ອຮັກສາການມີສ່ວນຮ່ວມຂອງລູກຄ້າ."

